Read on for my review on how you can win up to 200 times your bet and avail of free games with extra rewards!

What's the gameplay like for Kanga Cash?

Get comfortable and play the Kanga Cash slot without registration. With bets ranging from €1.00 to €20.00, the minimum stakes may be somewhat disappointing for high roller players. However, with an incredibly generous RTP of 96.13% and high volatility, who knows what could happen? The grand prizes, such as the fantastic jackpot, are found at the end of the Spin and Hold special feature, which has a Grand Jackpot of €15,000.00!

Nature-themed Symbols and Extra Features

The Kanga Cash online slot reels are filled with colorful symbols, including intricately decorated playing cards adorned with traditional Aboriginal art to fit the game's overall style. -Standard playing cards that pay out the least
-An eagle flying over the other symbols, paying out 0.5 times the bet when it appears on the first two reels or 30 times when it fills an entire pay line
-The word WILD overlaid on a map of Australia acts as any animal card or symbol and can complete winning lines, only appearing on reels 3, 4, and 5
-The kangaroo is the Scatter symbol, launching the extra Spin and Hold feature when it appears in three or more positions at once.

What are the Boomerang and Sunset symbols?

The Sunset icons, when they appear at least six times on the reels, will trigger the Spin and Hold bonus. The three central reels will initially get these Sunset Scatters, offering three free respins and transforming the Sunset icons into Sticky.

How can you win the Grand Bonus?

Now, for the grand prize – the Grand Bonus! There are two ways to win it:

-The Sunset icons must fill all the reels at the end of the feature
-The second way to win the Grand Bonus is randomly awarded while playing in paid mode.

My verdict on Kanga Cash

This free slot game is enjoyable, perfect for casual players who do not demand too much. However, it may not be the most suitable for high roller players. For a more intense experience, I recommend trying out Amazon Gold, another new slot game by Ainsworth, which is available in our library in both demo and paid modes.

Gameplay: Kanga Cash Extra without Download

Standard playing cards that pay less

Do you want to know how to win the biggest prize in the game – The Grand Bonus? You have two options:

Cover the reels with Sunset icons at the end of the feature.

My Verdict on Kanga Cash Extra
